flowchart LR
A[Client: Donate Form] --> B[POST /api/razorpay-order]
B --> C[Backend creates Razorpay order in INR]
C --> D[Client opens Razorpay checkout]
D --> E[POST /api/razorpay-verify]
E --> F[Razorpay Webhook to payment.captured/payment.failed]
F --> G[Verify webhook signature + persist event]
G --> H[Idempotent donation status transition]
H --> I[Generate receipt PDF with PDFKit]
I --> J[Upload receipt to Supabase Storage]
J --> K[Download static 80G document]
K --> L[Send email via Resend with attachments]
L --> M[Record email_deliveries status]
M --> N[Donor receives receipt in seconds]